// Template for local signing config.
//
// Copy this file to "Local.xcconfig" (which is gitignored) and set your own
// Apple Developer Team ID. Xcode reads it as the base configuration for the
// "OD App" target, so signing uses your team without committing it to the repo.
//
// Find your Team ID in Xcode > Settings > Accounts, or at
// https://developer.apple.com/account (Membership details).
//
// If this file is absent, the build still works: DEVELOPMENT_TEAM is simply
// unset and Automatic signing falls back to your selected team.
DEVELOPMENT_TEAM =
